{"title":"夏收之歌","authors":["李兴文"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏收之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李兴文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高高呀河弯弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社麦海接蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南风吹来翻金浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵麦香沁心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社麦海金浪翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪里歌声响连天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉白草帽漂浪面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼金浪变金山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱粒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风车响，珍珠落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风车唱着丰收歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦糠乘着东风扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场上珍珠堆成垛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场上珍珠堆成垛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粒粒珍珠乐心窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百张脸一副像："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒眉展颜笑呵呵。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}